title: The Club Cafe
typeOfFood: American, Organic, Thai, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A restaurant/deli, open to the public, is located within The Club SSI and offers some vegan choices for takeaway; vegans please inquire. The kitchen is open Mon, Tue and Thur evenings, however the takeaway items are available 7 days a week, anytime The Club is open. Simply ask the front desk staff to assist you.
